# 1) supabase.com → New project
# 2) Project Settings → API → copy URL + anon public key into .env (same folder as package.json)
# 3) SQL Editor → paste full file supabase/migrations/001_sessions.sql → Run
# 4) Authentication → Providers → Email ON (disable "Confirm email" for quick testing if you want)
# 5) Restart: npm run dev

